        <span style="font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);"><span style="color:#16a34a;">✓</span> Free Fixed-Price Survey</span>
        <span style="font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);"><span style="color:#16a34a;">✓</span> ECO4 Grants Assessed</span>
